name: Dr. Sarah Johnson
bio: Dr. Sarah Johnson has over 15 years of experience in general dentistry. She specializes in preventive care and is passionate about making dental visits comfortable for patients of all ages.

name: Dr. Michael Chen
bio: Dr. Michael Chen is a board-certified orthodontist with expertise in both traditional braces and clear aligner treatments. He stays updated with the latest orthodontic technologies.

name: Dr. Emily Rodriguez
bio: Dr. Emily Rodriguez specializes in pediatric dentistry and has a gentle approach that helps children feel at ease. She believes in creating positive dental experiences from an early age.

name: Dr. James Wilson
bio: Dr. James Wilson is an expert in cosmetic dentistry, offering services like teeth whitening, veneers, and smile makeovers. He combines artistry with dental science to create beautiful smiles.

name: Dr. Priya Patel
bio: Dr. Priya Patel is a specialist in endodontics, focusing on root canal treatments and saving natural teeth. She uses advanced techniques to ensure pain-free procedures.

name: Dr. Robert Martinez
bio: Dr. Robert Martinez specializes in periodontics, treating gum disease and performing dental implant procedures. He emphasizes the connection between oral health and overall wellness.

name: Dr. Lisa Thompson
bio: Dr. Lisa Thompson is a skilled oral surgeon with expertise in wisdom tooth extraction, jaw surgery, and dental implants. She prioritizes patient comfort and uses modern surgical techniques.

name: Dr. David Kim
bio: Dr. David Kim specializes in prosthodontics, creating custom dentures, bridges, and crowns. He focuses on restoring both function and aesthetics for patients with missing teeth.
